title: SolidWorks.2015.SP4.0-SSQ

In addition, starting with the new Collaborative Sharing feature, SOLIDWORKS 2015 enables access to Dassault SystemesÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ 3DEXPERIENCE platform and its cloud-based capabilities.
